<Key features>

<Each feature will be commonly named "bara" as easier reminder and simplicity.

/Hardware intercations:
  
  -Monitor light change:
    -Based on gps coordinates.
    -Average timing of productivity based on the light hours time of the location.

/Software interactions:

 *Activity remienders:
  -Eye relaxation movements.
  -Posture correction.
  -Arms and legs streching (light to high intervals)
  -Breating exercises (waking up or relaxion breaths), based on users actual energy levels.

 *Puntuation feedback in order to improve variations (age, location, gender, etnicity) recomendations.
  -Each accepted "bara"" to be tracked will create data, for predictions on users with posibility of giving it to a database for further optimization of other users.
